Name: Color
Description: CSS color name available in [matplotlib](https://matplotlib.org/stable/gallery/color/named_colors.html) (ex: `blue`) or hexadecimal code of color (ex: `#5234eb`).

Name: n
Description: Effective number of linear reservoir (Nash routing model)

Name: f_cpmax_Alias
Description: temporal factor for the `cpmax` parameter for LULC types (ex: `f_cpmax_Fs` where `Fs` is the LULC Alias for `Forest`)

Name: f_sfmax_Alias
Description: temporal factor for the `sfmax` parameter for LULC types (ex: `f_sfmax_Fs` where `Fs` is the LULC Alias for `Forest`)

Name: f_roots_Alias
Description: temporal factor for the `roots` parameter for LULC types (ex: `f_roots_Fs` where `Fs` is the LULC Alias for `Forest`)

Name: Min
Description: Minimum value of parameter in confidence interval

Name: Max
Description: Maximum value of parameter in confidence interval

Name: lulc
Description: Keyword for Land use and Land cover types

Name: hand
Description: Keyword for Height Above the Nearest Drainage
